      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey. i need to ask u something serious. i think i'm seeing glitches. i was in chicago yesterday and saw this exact same guy—same jacket, same limp, even the same coffee cup—and then today i'm in nyc and i see him again. like literally the same person. do u think we're hitting a resource limit or something? like the sim is running out of assets or whatever?",
